choices.text:
a taboo.

Though I can’t deny the true fact that a lot of Ghanaian ladies have experienced many (E-Abortion) even as we speak, due to pregnancy out of wedlock, due to societal expectation and many more reasons but, using the sword to arrest s*x-related problems cannot be a very good approach.

Why then is the police using the sword instead of the carrot? Is it because they are certified security officers or they are doing this because they are empowered to do so. As you read this article you will understand many things.

Recently, a video went viral with two men dressed in police uniforms forcefully dragging a Lady to be taken to the police station because, she had an abortion and used her boyfriend’s cutlass to kill the baby after the pregnancy. In the video, the suspect was heard telling the police that she used the knife only to assist in removing her placenta after the delivery of the baby.

She rather continued “I don’t understand why they have sent me to the police station because I used a knife to assist me deliver myself “. Police have become a terror in some regions of the country. This is very unfortunate!!Very sad!

Apart from the above statement by the lady. Some people quarreled that the police officers have no business controlling abortion. That the people who stole from the National food breed are still walking free with billions of dollars but when it comes to abortion, there is serious constant arrest and detention of women. Why??
